PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782290901
OL,3,CDozens dead in France as 'heat dome'
OL,4,Cbrings 40C temperatures to Europe
OL,6,FTransport has also been impacted, with
OL,7,FFrench rail company SNCF and Belgium's
OL,8,Ftrain provider SNCB cancelling trains
OL,9,Fdue to the heat, according to their
OL,10,Fwebsites.
OL,12,FWhat is a red warning?
OL,14,FThe Met Office says a red warning
OL,15,Fheatwave could pose a threat of
OL,16,F"serious illness or danger to life".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
