PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782290901
OL,3,CDozens dead in France as 'heat dome'
OL,4,Cbrings 40C temperatures to Europe
OL,6,FCurrent temperatures have been
OL,7,Fcompared to the August 2003 heatwave,
OL,8,Fwhen France saw the highest
OL,9,Ftemperatures in over half a century,
OL,10,Fand an estimated 15,000 people died.
OL,12,FThe Italian Ministry of Health has
OL,13,Fwarned people not to leave babies or
OL,14,Fanimals alone in vehicles during the
OL,15,Fheat, and urges people to wear
OL,16,Fsunscreen and breathable clothing.
OL,18,FWhy is Europe so hot?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
