FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782290901
OL,3,CDozens dead in France as 'heat dome'
OL,4,Cbrings 40C temperatures to Europe
OL,6,FHigh pressure is building over Europe,
OL,7,Ftrapping hot air, which then sinks and
OL,8,Flocks in the heat.
OL,10,FThis so-called "heat dome" is
OL,11,Fdominating weather systems in central
OL,12,Fand northwestern Europe, leading to
OL,13,Fextreme temperatures.
OL,15,FThe heat is expected to continue
OL,16,Fthroughout this week and even into
OL,17,FMonday.
OL,19,FCities like Cordoba in southern Spain
OL,20,Fwill continue to see temperatures in
OL,21,Fthe high 30Cs and early 40Cs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
